<p>What exactly syncs to my iCloud Keychain?&nbsp;How do I secure my Wi-Fi Network? How do I increase my Wi-Fi signal strength? Which wireless router should I get?&nbsp;Have you ever asked any of these questions? Even if you haven&#39;t, do you want to know the answers? Download today and listen as your two favorite geeks discuss and solve these issues and more. It&#39;s free!</p>
<p>[Note: Michael&#39;s schedule is such that he won&#39;t have timely time to convert the show to AAC and add the chapters this week, so 477 will only be available in MP3 format.]</p>
